@Diapolo
The SSL error that you get is weird, basically it mentions being unable to find a certificate. Which could mean that the needed certificate is missing on your computer. Though that would be strange as it worked before...

The OpenSSL faq mentions this error here: https://www.openssl.org/support/faq.html#USER5

